    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single displacement rate; this gap is accepted given the quasi-static nature of the COU and corroborating multi-laboratory experimental data. Quantitative validation metrics (percent difference, E/uval) satisfied for all three QoIs across both laboratories. Overall credibility sufficient for Medium model risk level and Medium decision consequence. Package accepted.",
